title: [PS3] Bakugan Battle Brawlers
description:
Where the toy and the cartoon collide! The world of Bakugan comes alive with the epic story of Good vs. Evil directed by the cartoon editor.

* The world of Bakugan comes alive: The arenas burst with incredible action and new play mechanics. It takes the Bakugan play experience to a whole new level.
* Epic storyline of Good vs. Evil directed by cartoon editor: Take your side in a brand new adventure and fight with Dan to defeat evil, save Vestroia and rescue Earth from total destruction with never before seen material!
* Create-a-brawler: Create and customize your own Bakugan Battle Brawler with unique attributes that will separate your Brawler from all others on the planet!
